      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "cool workaround. I, personally, would accept this one as best answer. Caveat: &lt;filename&gt; has to be defined for the system where the JVM is running, which makes a difference if you&#39;re remote debugging, in which case the file will be written on the remote system, not on the workstation where eclipse is running."
