    "body" : "<p>In the <strong>Variables</strong> view you right-click on the variable and select <strong>Change value</strong>. If your variable is huge you have to wait a few minutes (in this case Eclipse doesn't respond to commands) but in the end Eclipse will show your variable entirely.</p>\n"
