    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In Eclipse IDE 2020-09 it's &quot;Pretty print to console&quot; on right click.\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/zMyNe.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/zMyNe.png\" alt=\"Right Click dialog\" /></a></p>\n<p>From the console the copying is possible at full length.</p>\n"
  } ],
